 Health InsuranceJ Exchange Visitor Insurance RequirementsSuggested Health Insurance Companies Orientation All scholars must attend an orientation session after their arrival.  Register for a session with the J-1 advisor by emailing jinfo@unt.edu.  Orientation sessions are held most Thursdays at 10:00am.  Bring all immigration documents, local address and phone number, and proof of health insurance for you and any J-2 dependent(s) you brought with you to the U.S.  J-1 Immigration Advising If you would like to speak with an immigration advisor, here is our office information: Walk-in/Call-in Advising HoursMondays through Thursdays: 9:30-11:30am & 1:30-4:30pmFridays: 9:00am-12:00pmOffice Location: Marquis Hall, Room 110Telephone: 940-565-2195Email: jinfo@unt.eduPlease note that our office will still be open from 8:00am-5:00pm, Monday through Friday for document pick-ups and to accept normal requests, however advisors will only be available during the times listed above. TravelTravel Endorsements for J Visa HoldersTravel to Canada, Mexico and Contiguous Islands Extending Your DS-2019 Please contact your department about extending your program. Employment ResourcesSocial Security for J-1 and J-2 Visa HoldersIncidental Employment for J-1 Scholars Transfers Ending Your Program J-2 Dependent Resources J-2 DependentsJ-2 Dependent Employment Information for DepartmentsInviting a J-1 Exchange Visitor EventsUNT International CalendarUNT Calendars J World NewsletterSpring 2017 EditionFall 2016 Edition Visit Us Marquis Hall 1511 West Mulberry Street Marquis Hall, Room 105 Denton, TX 76201 Mail Us University of North Texas 1155 Union Circle, #311067 Denton, TX 76203-5017 USA Contact Us 940-565-2197 amanda.guccione@unt.edu Technical issues? Site last updated on May 08, 2017 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on 